<h3 id="head-110239ffbbd126ade3292572780c4f7e7bbab8d8"><a href="#bottom"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-bottom.png" alt="[BOTTOM]" height="10" width="14"></a><a href="#top"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-top.png" alt="[TOP]" height="10" width="14"></a>Barbarian</h3>
<p>
<a href="./Barbarian">Barbarian</a>s are hardy members of their race. They are fierce in combat, and their wrath is feared throughout the world. Combat is their life, and they learn to feel no fear. Barbarians are, however, suspicious of magic, which makes  magic devices fairly hard for them to use, and also makes it impossible for  them to play Mages. 
</p>

