<h3 id="head-2d015b626a67c4f736cc6c3a7cd912b9595aeb52"><a href="#bottom"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-bottom.png" alt="[BOTTOM]" height="10" width="14"></a><a href="#top"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-top.png" alt="[TOP]" height="10" width="14"></a>Hermit</h3>
<p>
<a href="./Hermit">Hermit</a>s live retired from the world. Spending long hours studying, they  weaken their physical side while they strengthen their spiritual powers.  Thus they get higher mana reserves but are much worse at physical combat. 
</p>

